snippet.title: Nine Parchments Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Nine Parchments is a co-operative blast 'em up game of magical mayhem from Frozenbyte! Available now on Nintendo Switch, Windows and PS4 (NA). The PS4 EU release is Dec 13th, and the Xbox One release date will be announced soon.

Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/nine-parchments-switch

PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP4029-CUSA05984_00-NINEPARCHMENTS00

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/471550/Nine_Parchments/

GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/nine_parchments

Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/nine-parchments

The Nintendo Switch version of Nine Parchments runs at 1080p/30fps docked and 720p/30fps undocked. The game supports local and online co-op with up to four players, as well as Local Wireless Play. One Joy-Con support is included as well.

The PS4 version of Nine Parchments runs at 1080/60fps and supports online and local co-op with up to four players.
